    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior retains a strong shine, though there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and small surface scratches consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, with only light wear on the driver's seat bolster and floor mats. Mechanically, it is sound, with a complete service history and all major systems functioning as intended. It offers a reliable and comfortable driving experience for someone looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle that has been treated with care.",
