    {
      "id": "sybil_20_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_20",
      "description": "Presented in pristine, showroom-quality condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. Meticulously maintained and free of any cosmetic or mechanical imperfections, it offers an uncompromising driving experience for the most discerning enthusiast. This is a rare opportunity to secure a definitive example of automotive excellence, curated for those who demand perfection.",
