      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_22_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_22",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe how gorgeous this car is. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept in mint condition and pampered like a member of the family. It looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or a speck of dust to be found! If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look, you're going to love it!",
      "price": 46500.0,
