    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_18_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54B32 power unit with its distinct individual throttle bodies and high-revving 8,000 RPM ceiling. This example boasts a flawless mechanical record: the double VANOS system has been overhauled, rod bearings replaced as preventative maintenance, and the rear subframe reinforced with precision gussets. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag six-speed manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry remains factory-spec with fresh bushings throughout, ensuring the telepathic handling and torsional rigidity these chassis are known for. A true turnkey masterpiece for the discerning purist.",
